<a href="/articles/27076.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27076/indexMediumPc2/27076.jpg?1463648792" alt="等了 4 年半，“五月天”终于要在明天发布新专辑了">
		
